HEADWORD: Filled cheese
<hw>Filled cheese</hw>. <def>An inferior kind of cheese made from skim
milk with a fatty ⟦ldquo⟧filling,⟦rdquo⟧ such as oleomargarine or lard,
to replace the fat removed in the cream.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

